					"value": "Main guard's dialog in Guard Tower in Cazador's Palace.\r\nTriggered automatically when you enter the tower, but also can be triggered by clicking on the guard. \r\nGuard is a female dwarf mesmerised to do the bidding of a powerful vampire. She speaks in a slightly dreamy tone."
